gainst fake companies, lists unregistered firmsCIPMN warns against financial waste in unregulated projectsMasisi had already granted the country of 2.3 million people half a day off to party on August 9.Tebogo is only the second African athlete to win an Olympic medal in the men's 200m, after Namibian Frankie Fredericks took silver in Atlanta in 1996.Botswana won their first Olympic medal at the 2012 London Games when Nijel Amos took silver in the 800m.\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 3545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1726, \"end\": 1731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.7140084098317173, \"rank\": 0.40054351544630534, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1860, \"end\": 1865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999999995443432, \"rank\": 3.816035966687136e-10, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 1885, \"end\": 1891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9665437332341005, \"rank\": 0.03313672193010008, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2384, \"end\": 2401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mokgweetsi Masisi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\"}, {\"begin\": 2462, \"end\": 2468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Masisi\", \"score\": 0.9999638801448353, \"rank\": 3.6121159774699597e-05, \"text\": \"Masisi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://